HazardCode is a BusinessClass
    owned by ic
    prefix is HAZ
    classic name is HAZARD

    Ontology
        symbolic key is HazardCode
            classic set name is HAZSET1

    Patterns
        implements StaticJava
        disable AuditIndex

    Persistent Fields

        Description
        Active      is Boolean
            classic name is ACTIVE-STATUS

    Conditions

        IsActive
        	restricted
            when (Active)

        IsInactive
        	restricted
            when (not Active)

        BypassRuleForTheseFiles
			restricted
	   		when (parentcontext.name = "PurchaseOrderEDIOutput")

    Attach Rules
        if (not BypassRuleForTheseFiles)
            constraint (Active)
		        "HazardCodeMustBeActive"
    
    Field Rules

        Description
            required

        Active
            initial value is true

